[Main]
This site is to provide a platform for users to search related stock information. Also, later on, user can communicate with each other, like twitter.

[Tools]
NodeJS to provide a basic HTTP server, combinding with JQuery, Coffee-script, high-charts, etc...
We need a database to save user information...MySQL?
We need a mail sending service to notify customer, we might use Sohu sendmail service at first.
For DNS, I will use DNSpod.
Now the project has a FQDN, www.taojkr.cc, a great start!
The project will be hold in github...

[Environment prepare]
1. Prepare install nodejs
2. Install Mongodb (Done)


